{"tid":1171270,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"做獸醫助護做左幾日，見證曬所有人情冷暖","createTime":"2019-05-25T14:54:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-01T04:28:33.000Z","uid":150836,"like":100,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"8a7bc6c9377598315b51b43769e4fbedd2c9799b","tid":1171270,"uid":150836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T14:54:44.000Z","msg":"今日見到一隻貓嚟做安樂死<br />\n個主人已經放棄左佢，<br />\n貓貓癱左，個主人就拎嚟啪，隻貓嚟到好似垃圾咁樣<br />\n又臭又痴立立，臨走嘅時候，連睇都唔想再睇一眼<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，<br />\n有隻狗仔心臟病發，嚟到冇曬呼吸心跳<br />\n個主人由頭陪到尾，喊到全世界都聽到<br />\n直至等到善終公司嚟送佢最後一程，火化當日仲會去陪佢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唉<br />\n有時真係好心寒<br />\n<br />\n點解可以咁狠心咁樣去對一個同你相處左10年嘅夥伴<br />\n人類果然係呢個世界最恐怖嘅生物"},{"pid":"cc830bf930ec8ba2894b4ec59fab351aa8b0e96e","tid":1171270,"uid":90672,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T14:57:23.000Z","msg":"可唔可以屌7果d仆街主人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46ed72e340a679e9f4d9bd11e477dcc7d0e8f5d5","tid":1171270,"uid":108236,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T15:12:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31c67319bc107396c9bfe4f770236f414e8f60e1","tid":1171270,"uid":239464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T15:13:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"48190c51ccdbfa6b6c097a21ffc09666a7e6e571","tid":1171270,"uid":150836,"like":29,"dislike":2,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"cc830bf930ec8ba2894b4ec59fab351aa8b0e96e","tid":1171270,"uid":90672,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T14:57:23.000Z","msg":"可唔可以屌7果d仆街主人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"ci